  "texts": [
    "A supervised graded exercise test to record volitional fatigue, risks or symptoms of ischemia was performed on a treadmill with the Bruce protocol before the 6-week intervention period.",
    "The test was done in non-fasting conditions and under medication.",
    "Electrocardiography was recorded continuously, and blood pressure was measured with an arm cuff every 3 min.",
    "Functional capacity in metabolic equivalent value (METs) was calculated.",
    "As a high proportion of participants with CAD are prescribed beta-blocker therapy, this relative method of exercise intensity considers the likely lower HRpeak achieved by these participants during the exercise test."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}